Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:28.76,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}舊校舍的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  聽說了嗎  舊校舍裡出現了幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽…靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  幽靈是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超喜歡妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼  這個你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所裡的花子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是謠言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊  幽靈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的聲音說著  出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有人聽見過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去確認下到底是不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…隨意進入舊校舍會不會有問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為班委的一員…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話不要多說  你也要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜  原來很害怕妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}妖~怪~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  說實話如果真有幽靈可就糟糕了  不太想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  但是作為男人  一定要保護小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那放學後大家一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又打算做什麼事情了呢  那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為風紀委員  不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樓關著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  二樓怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19\fad(200,200)}危險  別進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈先生  你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  不用主動去叫吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像從裡面傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是誰正在向我們走來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜…要由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我討厭H
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇  你到這來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  我只是因為這裡有很多舊書  來這裡看書的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫小闇  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚好滑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是禁止進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  是小唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連西連寺也一起來了究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還好是唯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然幽靈根本不可能存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  別這樣  發出詭異的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去  …
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…真的是幽靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰塵  好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想趁亂做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒什麼事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是絲毫也馬虎不得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你下次再敢做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…裡面傳來…鋼琴的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去  …
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去  …
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音是從哪裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對骷髏這樣太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  把頭還過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  這種時候也不知羞恥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  因為碰到了水  脫落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我暈不過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放開我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最…最強的的菈菈和闇影被…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  妖怪好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看他們都是從宇宙來的訪客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…不是幽靈啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我們都在本地星球被解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是在宇宙中飄蕩了無數年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺都聚在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是為了保護這個住所  鬧起了鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個有名的御門博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對這些孩子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就受了這麼點傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴比路克星的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和殺手金色闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不能這樣放任下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣放任下去  會給社會添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？無論如何請幫幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們介紹工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有辦法  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  平靜下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  還是沒有幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家能找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  我也可以安靜地生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西連寺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是做夢  絕對是做夢  一定是做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能夠暈過去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…啊  忘記自我介紹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是400年前死在這裡的小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗也該好好的打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們就算認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  不要說這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…況且說回來…你為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈也打哈欠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不能打哈欠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  說出來很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈還睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不能睡眠不足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡來的外星人每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  好想回家鄉星球去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說這麼沒骨氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為被解雇了所以就只能喝酒了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  今天也要大喝一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小聲一點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  和我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以好好的睡上一覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門博士  我們的新工作地點在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在郊外的帶大型停車場的宇宙鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}工程建設中  給您帶來不便請多諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在改建中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師  真是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠山先生  這裡以前不是宇宙鬼屋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…實際上發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙鬼屋倒閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人們也？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶大型停車場的宇宙鬼屋倒閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要改建成帶大型停車場的宇宙小酒館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不僱傭男外星人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在這裡住了400年的幽靈  叫小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要開始令人絕望的睡眠不足的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  明白什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜小姐是體質虛弱的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  沒什麼體力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠山那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠山？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友  也是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帶大型停車場的宇宙鬼屋的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是女外星人的話隨時都好僱傭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是女就可以被僱傭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把各位外星人變成女的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…小靜小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果可以變成女的的話真的想變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了工作什麼事都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  只要變成女的就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能變成女的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把外星人當傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類只要有心  大多數事情還是可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,措詞問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不清楚啊  在各種層面上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像是在開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我將教大家技藝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜小姐教大家技藝是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技藝是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算把我會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三絃琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先瞭解少女的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就能瞬息萬變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是把外星人變成能唱會跳的人妖外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看上去很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  正如公主所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是這種氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}加油啊  好  加油啊  好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存下去  什麼都得做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜小姐  那我也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就開始練習了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東南西北  來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東南西北
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜老師  您明明是古代的人  居然也會鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在這個校舍裡住了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  如果在這時候放棄了  不就又變回昨天的我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白  我們已經不是昨天的我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對  從舉止到內心  都要變成少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  來  練習內八字走路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠山先生  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們身上有很好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再使把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  從今天開始能在我店裡工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  全部錄用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我也可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進  請進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜小姐也被錄用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  作為這家店的「媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人的朋友也來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王是誰～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}一種抽籤遊戲  其他人要聽從抽到王簽的人任何要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要和大王接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩斯丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  接到快遞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面是宇宙鹹鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  這個和飯一起吃最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海膽和粕汁也很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}粕汁：將酒粕溶到日式高湯中所形成的湯品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有醬炒蔬菜鮭魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼  好想吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  特地從宇宙寄來鹹鮭魚  真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:24:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到鹹鮭魚還是地球的  尤其是日本的北海道的好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  地球產的更好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地球的特產就決定帶鹹鮭魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  To  LOVEる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  為什麼猿山冒出來了
